original_title: The 8th Anniversary AKINA EAST LIVE INDEX-XXIII
overview: Akina Nakamori's 8th anniversary live concert video which was previously released in 1989 on VHS and laserdisc. Filmed in April '89, and contains 24 songs, including all her single released songs starting with her debut Slow Motion, up to LIAR. Other songs include DESIRE, Shojo A, and more.
title: The 8th Anniversary AKINA EAST LIVE INDEX-XXIII
